# Payo Frontend Configuration
# This project is a static vanilla SPA served via 'npx serve'.
# It does NOT use Vite's build step, so VITE_API_URL is not applicable.
#
# The API URL is injected directly via window.PAYO_API_URL in index.html.
# Update that value in index.html before deploying to a new environment.
#
# For reference:
PAYO_API_URL=https://payo-payroll-automation-system-production.up.railway.app/api
